data.description: 2021 Adams Home, Model1515. Location, Location and Location. Just minutes to UWF, West Florida Hospital and all of the shopping that one could ask for. Plus a 12 minute drive to the airport. As you approach this home, Come in and see this virtually new, upgraded 3/2 craftsman style home located in Cardinal Cove. You’ll love this cozy cottage with an spacious design and trey ceilings creating a feeling of being home. The living room is roomy, as you walk into the kitchen and dining room, the kitchen highlights stainless appliances and upgraded custom-built bead board shaker cabinets accented with brushed nickel hardware. The master features a walk-in closet and a large bath with double vanity, shower/tub combo and a shelved alcove. The additional bedrooms are split- planned for privacy and features a full hall bathroom, linen closet, coat closet and laundry room. Enjoy relaxing in your screened back porch enjoying the privacy of the backyard with utility shed, landscaping and an irrigation system. Measurements are estimates please verify.
